<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77e677dd-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460ss–6"><num value="460ss–6">§ 460ss–6.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">As used in this subchapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id77e677de-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460ss–6/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “program” means the Klamath River Basin Conservation Area Restoration Program established under <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s460ss–1/b">section 460ss–1(b) of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id77e677df-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460ss–6/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “Secretary” means the Secretary of the Interior.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="id77e677e0-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/99/552/s7">Pub. L. 99–552, § 7</ref>, <date date="1986-10-27">Oct. 27, 1986</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/100/3086">100 Stat. 3086</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
